text: Dario Vangeli (born 3 January 1988) is an Italian male boxer twice world champion, in 2011 and 2015, at the World Police and Fire Games. ==References== ==External links== * Dario Vangeli at Fiamme Oro Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male boxers Category:Boxers of Fiamme Oro Category:Light-welterweight boxers
